text: Mohamed Mukhesur Rahman (born 1 February 1970) is a Bangladeshi swimmer. He competed in the 200 m breaststroke at the 1992 Summer Olympics, Rahman finished in 52nd place in the heats so didn't advance any further. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Bangladeshi male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Bangladesh Category:Swimmers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
